imdb.plot outline: Matt had two clients - Outsider and Calvin - oh and they're all dead. So we travel to the afterlife as the deceased have a conversation with the man himself - Jesus. Life for them was all about championships, money, and sex, but that is all no more. It's time for them to confess their sins as we are treated to a recap of their final days and for one important question to be answered - how did they die?
